                                  auto-complete ac-nrepl
                                  ace-jump-mode
                                  htmlize
                                  paredit undo-tree
                                  markdown-mode yaml-mode
                                  tramp magit multiple-cursors rainbow-delimiters
                                  color-theme-sanityinc-solarized color-theme-sanityinc-tomorrow color-theme-solarized)
